gemorna-utr-pred-nutshell — non-commercial research license
===========================================================

The gemorna-utr-pred-nutshell pipeline wraps and bundles upstream tools whose
license restricts commercial use:

  • GEMORNA (RainaBio) — non-commercial research only

Because gemorna-utr-pred-nutshell is a derivative work of GEMORNA and reproduces
its assets (model checkpoints, vocabulary, source code via Apptainer image), the
COMPOSITE work — including the wrapper code in this repository — inherits
GEMORNA's restriction. The text of GEMORNA's license is reproduced verbatim
in THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md and must travel with any copy of this repository
or its build artefacts (.sif image, Docker image, etc.).

In particular, by accessing, downloading, or using this pipeline you agree:

  1. To use it solely for non-commercial research purposes (per GEMORNA).
  2. Not to redistribute it (or any derivative work) to third parties for a
     fee, except as necessary to publish academic research in accordance with
     standard academic practice.
  3. To retain this LICENSE file and THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md in every copy
     and modification.
  4. To cite the upstream GEMORNA paper in any academic work that uses
     results produced by this pipeline.

For commercial use, contact the GEMORNA corresponding author
(caojicong@rainabio.com) to obtain a separate commercial license.

